        - weight: 60
          module:
          - rid: 107151359355650148
          output: 'A nocturnal visit is all it takes for the director to abandon
            his patrons. Our men can be so persuasive when the need arises... it
            is their trade, after all!

            [Gained 5 Bliss]

'
        - weight: 40
          module:
          - rid: 107151359355650149
          - rid: 107151359355650150
          output: 'The gall of this man! Even with a band of fanatics appearing at
            his doorstep, he refuses to forsake his benefactors. Such dedication
            would be commendable were it not directed squarely against us.

            [Lost
            20 Zeal & 10 Bliss]

'
